&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Valo Health is a human-centric, AI-enabled biotechnology company working to make new drugs for patients faster. The company’s Opal Computational Platform transforms drug discovery and development through a unique combination of&amp;nbsp;real-world data, AI, human translational models and predictive chemistry.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
