&lt;li&gt;Design, prioritize, and execute focused and diverse compound libraries to address SAR hypotheses and project needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement parallel synthesis strategies to enable rapid library generation and iteration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and optimize synthetic routes that allow efficient diversification and scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Medicinal Chemistry, In vitro Pharmacology, Biology, DMPK, ML/AI, and Chemistry Data Science teams to guide compound design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply structure–activity relationship (SAR) insights to drive compound optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize modern approaches such as high-throughput experimentation (HTE)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform compound synthesis, purification, and characterization (e.g., NMR, LC-MS) of intermediates for library synthesis on 1-5g scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document experimental work and communicate results through presentations and reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
