&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ph.D. (or equivalent experience) in Organic Chemistry, Medicinal Chemistry, or related field &lt;em&gt;(or M.S. with 4–6+ years, B.S. with 6–8+ years relevant experience)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong expertise in synthetic organic chemistry within a drug discovery setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience in compound library design and synthesis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li

